凡事皆有因果
What goes around comes around.

269
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:43,940
貨車還在, 他們一定在附近
BLACK: The truck's still here, Axminster.

270
00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:44,365
They got to be close.

271
