我跟媽在感恩節時最想你
You know, I think Mom and I missed you most

272
00:21:51,843 --> 00:21:54,209
around Thanksgiving, Christmas.

273
00:21:53,052 --> 00:21:54,254
還有聖誕節

274
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:58,007
我記得你會帶我去砍樹
I remember you used to take me out to cut a tree.

275
00:21:57,991 --> 00:21:59,481
別煩了
Stop riding it!

276
00:21:59,490 --> 00:22:01,460
我來這裡讓你那麼難受嗎？
Is my being here

277
00:22:00,752 --> 00:22:01,776
that hard on you?

278
00:22:01,694 --> 00:22:03,218
孩子
Bud,

279
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,646
這話題到此為止
subject is closed.

280
00:22:20,739 --> 00:22:22,206
( fishing line creaking )

281
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:23,535
我釣到了
I got one.

282
00:22:24,718 --> 00:22:26,208
我釣到了
I got one!

283
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:30,576
拉上來, 孩子, 小心
JACKSON: I said drag, bud. Watch it.

284
00:22:30,724 --> 00:22:32,425
真不錯
Ah, that's a beaut!

285
00:22:32,690 --> 00:22:34,530
晚餐, 別讓牠溜了

286
00:22:32,851 --> 00:22:33,579
That's for dinner.

