00:22:33,685 --> 00:22:34,811
Don't let loose of him.

288
00:22:34,961 --> 00:22:36,714
我不會讓牠溜了
I'm not gonna let loose of him.

289
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,100
拿網子來, 哈利
Get the net, Harry.

290
00:22:41,927 --> 00:22:42,723
( gunshot )

291
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:43,970
搞什麼…

292
00:22:42,828 --> 00:22:43,453
Hey, what the...?

293
00:22:43,562 --> 00:22:44,551
( gunshots )

294
00:22:44,863 --> 00:22:45,625
Aah!

295
00:22:46,298 --> 00:22:49,199
( gunshots )

296
00:22:55,974 --> 00:22:57,709
究竟怎麼回事？
What the hell is goin' on?

297
00:22:57,709 --> 00:22:59,179
我等一下跟你說, 快
I'll tell you later. Come on.

298
00:22:59,180 --> 00:23:00,276
你的朋友是誰？
Who are your friends?

299
00:23:00,390 --> 00:23:02,073
