Harry, I didn't think they'd find me here.

300
00:23:02,022 --> 00:23:03,890
他們可能很快就過來了
They'll probably be down here in a minute.

301
00:23:07,193 --> 00:23:08,294
我們走
Let's go!

302
00:23:19,172 --> 00:23:20,958
蘆葦？
JACKSON: Hollow reeds?

303
00:23:21,733 --> 00:23:22,859
MacGYVER: Yeah. We'll make 'em think

304
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:24,560
對, 要讓他們以為 我們還在水裡
we're still out there in the water.

305
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:27,880
他們會識破的
They're too smart for that one, boy.

306
00:23:28,250 --> 00:23:29,568
總是要試試
Got to try something.

307
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:32,039
如果他們真的中計呢, 孩子？
What if they do fall for this stunt of yours, bud?

308
00:23:32,020 --> 00:23:33,379
對我們有什麼好處？
What do we get out of it?

309
00:23:33,380 --> 00:23:35,080
拉開距離
Buy a little distance.

310
00:23:36,289 --> 00:23:39,626
