They tricked us.

320
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:29,169
什麼意思？
What are you talking about?

321
00:24:29,170 --> 00:24:30,700
被馬蓋先設計了
MacGyver set us up.

322
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,171
我們去跟阿克斯特說
Let's go tell Axminster.

323
00:24:41,087 --> 00:24:44,056
看來你的朋友在湖的對岸 找到那些蘆葦

324
00:24:41,213 --> 00:24:42,441
Guess your friends found those reeds

325
00:24:42,547 --> 00:24:43,946
