00:25:00,974 --> 00:25:02,829
我就是在想那類的東西
I was thinking along those lines.

335
00:25:03,068 --> 00:25:03,796
Ah.

336
00:25:20,660 --> 00:25:22,414
哈利, 我們唯一的問題
The only problem we got, Harry,

337
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:25,798
要把他們擊昏, 得要射得準

338
00:25:22,854 --> 00:25:24,378
in order for me to knock them out,

339
00:25:24,489 --> 00:25:25,956
I'm gonna have to hit them just right.

340
00:25:25,799 --> 00:25:27,418
正中頸子
Right in the neck.

341
00:25:29,469 --> 00:25:30,637
要是射偏了呢？
What if you miss?

342
00:26:06,965 --> 00:26:08,240
好, 給我
Okay, here we go.

343
00:26:09,509 --> 00:26:11,092
現在吹箭有了
HARRY: Now we got a blow gun,

344
00:26:11,010 --> 00:26:14,194
也許做些腳印 引他們找到我們
maybe help to make kind of a trail for them to track us.

345
00:26:21,490 --> 00:26:23,960
等一下, 他們的足跡通往小溪

346
00:26:21,546 --> 00:26:22,376
BLACK: Hold it.

347
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,277
Their trail leads down to the stream.

348
00:26:40,031 --> 00:26:42,090
怎麼回事？
Hey, what's the matter?

349
00:26:42,334 --> 00:26:44,063
Hey, hey, what's...?

350
00:26:43,410 --> 00:26:44,610
怎麼…

351
00:26:44,869 --> 00:26:48,498
( grunting )

352
00:26:49,641 --> 00:26:51,268
( yells )

353
00:26:58,091 --> 00:26:59,214
做得好
Nice.

354
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,350
要正中目標才對
Gotta hit them just right.

355
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,100
