Don't seem to have a lot of choice.

357
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:05,655
是沒有
No.

358
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:21,200
等一下
Hold it!

359
00:27:21,506 --> 00:27:22,666
Hold it right there, bud.

360
00:27:21,570 --> 00:27:23,780
等等, 孩子, 你停不停啊？

361
00:27:22,774 --> 00:27:23,798
Will you stop?

362
