I ain't moving until I get an answer.

367
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,480
抱歉, 哈利, 我不該來的
I'm sorry, Harry.

368
00:27:38,890 --> 00:27:40,016
I shouldn't have come.

369
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:41,950
