I underestimated some things.

370
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:44,585
回答我的問題就好
Just answer the question.

371
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:49,770
這跟自由與和平有關, 哈利

372
00:27:46,698 --> 00:27:47,255
It has to do

373
00:27:47,365 --> 00:27:49,925
