And some people who don't like either.

375
00:27:57,201 --> 00:28:00,546
我希望這值得那尾溜掉的鱒魚

376
00:27:57,375 --> 00:27:58,342
Well, I sure hope

377
00:27:58,443 --> 00:28:00,604
it's worth losing that damn trout.

378
00:28:06,551 --> 00:28:08,610
他們還活著, 阿克斯特
They're still alive, Axminster.

379
00:28:08,620 --> 00:28:10,447
-要把他們拉上來嗎？ -別管了

380
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,482
Shall we pick them up?

381
00:28:09,587 --> 00:28:10,485
AXMINSTER: Forget them.

382
00:28:10,448 --> 00:28:11,816
走吧
Move it.

383
00:28:13,284 --> 00:28:15,083
有正事要辦
We got a job to do.

384
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:20,492
附近有林務站嗎？
Is there a ranger station around?

385
00:28:22,330 --> 00:28:24,870
還是林火瞭望台、農場什麼的

386
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,560
How about a fire lookout,

387
