00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,451
We'll swing around the hill and meet you.

400
00:28:43,381 --> 00:28:44,613
好
CARSON: Right.

401
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:50,620
打從兩年前被灰熊追之後…

402
00:28:48,626 --> 00:28:49,650
HARRY: Haven't done this much running

403
00:28:49,761 --> 00:28:52,127
就沒這麼跑過了
since two winters ago when a grizzly was chasing me.

404
00:28:52,624 --> 00:28:53,855
牠有抓到你嗎？
Did he catch you?

405
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:56,228
沒有, 牠追鵟追累了
HARRY: Nah, got tired trying to catch an old buzzard.

406
00:28:56,561 --> 00:28:59,264
你在做什麼？停下來撿石頭？

407
00:28:56,835 --> 00:28:57,927
Hey, what are you doing now?

408
00:28:58,103 --> 00:28:59,331
Stop to collect rocks?

409
00:29:05,236 --> 00:29:06,502
也許是那邊
CARSON: Maybe up that way.

410
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:08,778
好, 把他們逼出來
AXMINSTER: Okay, we'll flush them out.

411
00:29:09,548 --> 00:29:10,739
看到什麼了嗎？
See anything?

412
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,576
我看到很多東西
MacGYVER: Oh, I see a lot of things.

413
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:14,620
有什麼是我感興趣的嗎？
Anything I'd be interested in?

414
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,780
有

