00:29:14,986 --> 00:29:17,853
兩輛吉普車分開
Yeah. Two jeeps splitting up.

416
00:29:17,980 --> 00:29:20,480
其中一輛往這邊來了 但還要一陣子才會到

417
00:29:18,089 --> 00:29:19,181
Only one's heading our way,

418
00:29:19,290 --> 00:29:19,984
but he's gonna be

419
00:29:20,091 --> 00:29:22,452
我想我們還有點時間
a while getting here, so I figure we got a little time.

