00:43:16,560 --> 00:43:18,824
( man grunts )

657
00:43:22,235 --> 00:43:23,857
逮到他了
Got him good.

658
00:43:24,270 --> 00:43:25,340
是啊
Yeah.

659
00:43:38,650 --> 00:43:40,816
還有阿克斯特
We still have Axminster.

660
00:43:41,390 --> 00:43:43,521
不過這次我們佔優勢了
Only this time, we got the odds.

661
00:43:43,991 --> 00:43:45,213
對
Yeah.

662
00:43:51,528 --> 00:43:52,460
Ow!

