665
00:43:58,602 --> 00:43:59,967
( gunshot )

666
00:44:06,980 --> 00:44:09,074
再過去一點, 孩子
Try, try to move him over, bud.

667
00:44:09,913 --> 00:44:11,904
( grunting )

668
00:44:13,050 --> 00:44:14,290
就是現在, 孩子
Now, bud!

669
00:44:16,720 --> 00:44:18,415
( yelling )

670
00:44:23,100 --> 00:44:24,554
你還好嗎, 孩子？
You all right, bud?

671
00:44:25,260 --> 00:44:27,227
我好得很, 哈利
I'm more than all right, Harry.

672
00:44:31,735 --> 00:44:32,929
( groans )

673
00:44:34,471 --> 00:44:35,495
Whew!

674
00:44:35,873 --> 00:44:37,670
