675
00:44:40,044 --> 00:44:42,069
你有打算要再來嗎？
You figuring on coming back this way?

676
00:44:41,980 --> 00:44:43,305
一定會的
Count on it.

677
00:44:43,984 --> 00:44:45,547
我會期待的
I'll look forward to it.

678
00:44:46,286 --> 00:44:47,714
我也是
Me, too.

679
00:45:08,475 --> 00:45:09,934
哈利
Hey, Harry...

680
00:45:10,810 --> 00:45:12,909
你要抓到那尾鱒魚, 好嗎？
catch that big old trout, will you?

681
00:45:14,150 --> 00:45:15,472
一定會的
Count on it.

682
00:45:19,550 --> 00:45:21,408
好好保重, 孩子
Take care of yourself, bud.

